name: AVAudioConverterInputStatus
desc: An option that indicates the status of an audio converter input block.

items.name: case endOfStream
items.desc: A status that indicates you’re at the end of an audio stream.

items.name: case haveData
items.desc: A status that indicates the normal case where you supply data to the converter.

items.name: case noDataNow
items.desc: A status that indicates you’re out of data.
